You are using a container image for a cloud deployment and are building a stateful applica-tion that must store data between deployments. Which type of storage should be used?
A)  Ephemeral volume
B)  Bridged volume
C)  Container image
D)  Persistent volume
D
D. A persistent volume, sometimes called persistent storage, keeps data between deploy-ments of the virtualized environment. A container image is used for the original boot.
